  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/2fa7afedeedc1988c77d15d0656856d2.poster.avif?t=1750972346\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/2fa7afedeedc1988c77d15d0656856d2.webm?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/2fa7afedeedc1988c77d15d0656856d2.mp4?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>She is the dark magician, an apostle of the great Kraken Nialato. <br>From this moment, she hunts to offer living sacrifices for Nialato.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Let’s hunt humans and collect clothing.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/cf480bebf551c3a5eccb1c47ea0588a4.poster.avif?t=1750972346\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/cf480bebf551c3a5eccb1c47ea0588a4.webm?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/cf480bebf551c3a5eccb1c47ea0588a4.mp4?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Kraken likes people dressed in pretty clothes. <br>Collect various outfits to please the great Kraken.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple and highly action-packed action. </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/1e090855c82acb570799f89d4cebf458.poster.avif?t=1750972346\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/1e090855c82acb570799f89d4cebf458.webm?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/1e090855c82acb570799f89d4cebf458.mp4?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game controls and systems are very simple and easy. <br>And the intense action immerses you in the hunt for foolish people.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Insignificant humans call for a “physical education” class.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/b8f90a2434feb03a69e9589b09771900.poster.avif?t=1750972346\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/b8f90a2434feb03a69e9589b09771900.webm?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/b8f90a2434feb03a69e9589b09771900.mp4?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The training begins with wrestling because using the Kraken <br>on foolish humans is a luxury.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tie up the living sacrifices with the power of the Kraken.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/bb8ef01d5472176b5e90195a16622d77.poster.avif?t=1750972346\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/bb8ef01d5472176b5e90195a16622d77.webm?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/bb8ef01d5472176b5e90195a16622d77.mp4?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Summon the Kraken at the right moment to bind the humans. <br>Obtain lots of valuable rewards from the captured living sacrifices.",
